Phyllis Hill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phyllis_Hill 0 Phyllis Hill (October 27, 1920 – January 1, 1993) was an American dancer and actress.Hill's mother was actress Peggy Johnson Hill. Her sister, Joyce Hill Rainier, danced with the Monte Carlo Ballets Russes.Hill began her career in the late 1940s, appearing on stage and in small television roles in New York.
